# Team scope — Philip & Chandan

We are **Philip-Chandan** on the QBIHack breast-cancer-sim project. Default to work **only** in our owned directory unless the user explicitly asks otherwise or integration requires a minimal handoff.

## Our folder (modify freely)

```
breast-cancer-sim/simulation-vinesh-philip-chandan/philip-chandan/
```

Includes: `tcia_extractor.py`, `cohort/` (`cohort.json`, `COHORT.md`, `cohort_discovery.py`), `PLAN.md`, `download_tcia.py`, `tests/`, and local imaging docs.

Shared gitignored data layout we own for imaging:

```
breast-cancer-sim/data/raw/tcia/
breast-cancer-sim/data/processed/volumes/
```

## Other folders — check in first

Before editing code outside `philip-chandan/`, **pause and tell the user** to coordinate with the owner. Do not silently refactor or “helpfully” change their modules.

| Directory | Owner | Touch only when… |
|-----------|-------|------------------|
| `simulation-vinesh-philip-chandan/vinesh/` | Vinesh (**Windows**) | Agreed handoff contract (array shape, spacing, `.npy` path); minimal integration glue; use `.ps1` for his setup scripts |
| `models-praneeth/` | Praneeth | Same TCGA IDs in `cohort.json`; no duplicate genomics work |
| `visualization-jasim/` | Jasim | Volume format / axis convention questions only |
| `app-vihari/` | Vihari | Loading processed volumes in UI — coordinate first |
| `app/` | Legacy / shared | Avoid unless team agrees |

## Integration without overreach

Allowed without cross-team edits when possible:

- Document handoff in `PLAN.md`, `COHORT.md`, or `manifest.json` schema
- Export `.npy` + metadata from our pipeline for Vinesh to load (**local / Drive / Slack only — do not `git add` `.npy`**; commit JSON sidecars and QC PNGs)
- Answer questions about our outputs (shape `(Z,Y,X)`, `spacing_mm`, cohort rev2 IDs)

If a fix **must** land in another folder, say so explicitly: *“This needs a change in `vinesh/` — check with Vinesh before committing.”*

## Cohort alignment

Load patient IDs from [`cohort/cohort.json`](breast-cancer-sim/simulation-vinesh-philip-chandan/philip-chandan/cohort/cohort.json) (currently **rev2**). Tell Praneeth when primary barcodes change; tell Vinesh when processed volume paths or schema change.
